    "Each sequence is a pair of X and corresponding y as given in Eq. 1.",
    "If T is the input length and H is the forecasting horizon, X can be given by X = {x 1, x 2, x 3, …, x T } and y can be repre- sented as y = {y 1, y 2, y 3, …, y H }.",
